houseItems.name: Stainless Steel Cookware Set
houseItems.description: Upgrade your kitchen with the KitchenPro Stainless Steel Cookware Set. Crafted with high-quality stainless steel, this set is durable and easy to clean. With a variety of pots and pans, it covers all your cooking needs.

houseItems.name: Cotton Bed Sheet Set
houseItems.description: Indulge in the comfort of the ComfortLiving Cotton Bed Sheet Set. Made from 100% pure cotton, it offers a soft and cozy feel for a good night's sleep. The stylish design adds elegance to your bedroom.

houseItems.name: Multifunctional Vacuum Cleaner
houseItems.description: Keep your home spotless with the CleanMaster Multifunctional Vacuum Cleaner. Its powerful motor ensures effective cleaning, while the HEPA filter traps dust and allergens. The versatile design allows dry and wet cleaning.

houseItems.name: Wooden Dining Table Set
houseItems.description: Gather your family for meals around the ElegantHome Wooden Dining Table Set. Crafted from solid wood, this set exudes timeless elegance and durability. The comfortable chairs ensure a delightful dining experience.

houseItems.name: LED Smart TV
houseItems.description: Experience entertainment like never before with the SmartVision LED Smart TV. Its vibrant display and smart connectivity open up a world of streaming possibilities. The built-in Chromecast allows seamless casting of your favorite content.

houseItems.name: Eco-Friendly Dustbin
houseItems.description: Promote sustainability with the GreenEarth Eco-Friendly Dustbin. Made from recycled plastic, it is environmentally responsible. The odor-blocking lid keeps your surroundings fresh and clean.

houseItems.name: Ayurvedic Aloe Vera Soap
houseItems.description: Pamper your skin with the goodness of Ayurvedic Aloe Vera Soap by HerbEssentials. Enriched with natural ingredients, this soap nourishes and hydrates your skin, leaving it soft and supple.

houseItems.name: Sustainable Bamboo Toothbrush
houseItems.description: Switch to an eco-friendly oral care routine with the EcoSmiles Sustainable Bamboo Toothbrush. The biodegradable handle and soft bristles make it gentle on your teeth and the environment.

houseItems.name: Premium Cotton Bath Towel Set
houseItems.description: Wrap yourself in luxury with the CozyBath Premium Cotton Bath Towel Set. Made from soft and absorbent cotton, these towels provide ultimate comfort after a relaxing bath.

houseItems.name: Handcrafted Terracotta Planter
houseItems.description: Add a touch of nature to your home with the NatureHues Handcrafted Terracotta Planter. Its rustic charm and porous material promote healthy plant growth.

houseItems.name: Durable Stainless Steel Clothes Rack
houseItems.description: Keep your clothes organized with the HomeOrganize Stainless Steel Clothes Rack. Its sturdy design and ample hanging space make it a perfect addition to your laundry room.

houseItems.name: Energy-Efficient LED Bulbs
houseItems.description: Illuminate your space with the energy-efficient BrightLight LED Bulbs. These long-lasting bulbs offer bright and clear illumination while reducing your electricity consumption.
